26:17.923 --> 26:21.506
- Just like
regular white people.

26:21.589 --> 26:23.881
- Did this whites happen to tell
you where they were heading?

26:23.964 --> 26:27.005
- No, man, fuck you think?
People don't say shit to me.

26:27.089 --> 26:28.881
- Perhaps that's because
of the customer service.

26:28.964 --> 26:31.047
- Is this little boy your son?
- I'm fully grown.

26:31.130 --> 26:33.047
Thank you.
I'm an adult man.

26:33.130 --> 26:34.964
- Okay, well, uh,
y'all want a room or what?

26:35.047 --> 26:37.631
- No, we don't want a room!
We want answers!

26:37.714 --> 26:40.089
Fucking guy thinks
I'm old enough to be your daddy.

26:40.172 --> 26:41.089
Jesus H.

26:41.172 --> 26:43.756
- Well, you are
aging horrifically.

26:43.839 --> 26:45.339
Look, Jesse,
I know you're disappointed,

26:45.422 --> 26:47.297
but I think it's for the best.

26:47.381 --> 26:48.923
I don't know what
you're capable of.

26:49.005 --> 26:51.547
I don't want our paths to cross
with those guys ever again.

26:51.631 --> 26:55.130
- Shit, maybe that's that.

26:55.214 --> 26:59.005
- [sighs]
No, I don't think so.

27:02.130 --> 27:03.381
[clay shatters]

27:05.172 --> 27:07.005
[machine whirs]

27:08.172 --> 27:10.172
[gunshot]

27:11.422 --> 27:12.964
- Damn it.

27:13.047 --> 27:16.005
- You're leading too much.

27:16.089 --> 27:17.130
- Funny.

27:17.214 --> 27:19.422
I wasn't having any trouble
'fore you got here.

27:19.506 --> 27:20.964
- You know,
I would have come with you

27:21.047 --> 27:23.631
if you wanted to shoot 'em
like we used to together.

27:23.714 --> 27:25.589
- You're the one who stopped,
not me.

27:27.714 --> 27:29.964
- I'm sorry, baby.

27:30.047 --> 27:33.631
I'm so sorry that I didn't
tell you I was talking to him.

27:33.714 --> 27:36.422
I never should have
kept that from you.

27:36.506 --> 27:38.130
- I agree.

27:38.214 --> 27:40.130
Can't keep secrets from family.
It's not right.

27:40.214 --> 27:42.756
- No.
No more.

27:42.839 --> 27:44.422
- Deal.

27:44.506 --> 27:46.714
- Deal.
Come here.

27:50.130 --> 27:53.005
[Beethoven's
"Moonlight Sonata"]

27:53.089 --> 27:54.631
Ooh.

27:54.714 --> 28:01.756
♪ ♪

28:29.714 --> 28:32.005
- Good afternoon, Jesus.

28:32.089 --> 28:36.381
Thank you for watching after
my family and myself.

28:36.464 --> 28:38.547
And thank you for letting me
be born into this world

28:38.631 --> 28:40.005
as a Gemstone.

28:40.089 --> 28:42.297
- [grunts]

28:42.381 --> 28:44.047
[strained shouting]

28:44.130 --> 28:45.297
[weights rattle]

28:45.381 --> 28:47.714
- The legacy of my family
carries immense weight...

28:47.798 --> 28:48.881
- [panting]

28:48.964 --> 28:52.005
- But I take it you are no
stranger to that, Dear Lord.

28:52.089 --> 28:54.381
♪ ♪

28:54.464 --> 28:56.547
- [panting] We gotta get off
the compound, baby.

28:56.631 --> 28:58.547
[frenzied breathing]

28:58.631 --> 29:00.547
Oh, take me right here.

29:00.631 --> 29:02.381
- My duties are great,

29:02.464 --> 29:05.589
but many are the pleasures
you have bestowed upon me.

29:05.673 --> 29:07.506
- Oh, no.

29:07.589 --> 29:09.005
I came.

29:09.089 --> 29:11.673
[panting]
I'm so sorry.

29:14.839 --> 29:17.839
[snake hissing]

29:19.881 --> 29:21.589
- Grant me strength,
Dear Lord,

29:21.673 --> 29:24.005
to lead the people...

29:26.381 --> 29:28.714
To bring them
to your righteous kingdom.

29:28.798 --> 29:34.547
♪ ♪

29:34.631 --> 29:35.923
And thank you, Lord,

29:36.005 --> 29:38.422
for forgiving me
of my wrongdoings,

29:38.506 --> 29:40.631
which you know
are not who I am.

29:40.714 --> 29:43.214
Your ability to accept me
for the sinner I am

29:43.297 --> 29:46.422
only speaks
to your greatness...

29:46.506 --> 29:51.631
[sighs]
His righteous grace...

29:51.714 --> 29:56.923
Your guidance and mercy is all
that the Gemstones require.

29:57.005 --> 30:00.339
Please, teach me your patience.

30:00.422 --> 30:01.839
[doorbell rings]
Teach--

30:01.923 --> 30:03.881
[music stops]

30:03.964 --> 30:06.547
Fuckin' A.

30:06.631 --> 30:08.089
Somebody get the door, please.

30:10.714 --> 30:12.130
[doorbell rings]
Get the door!

30:12.214 --> 30:14.381
I'm praying, God damn it!

30:17.839 --> 30:20.506
- Hey, Mama.

30:20.589 --> 30:21.506
I'm home.

30:21.589 --> 30:24.464
- Gideon.
Oh, my baby.

30:24.547 --> 30:27.798
[both laugh]

30:27.881 --> 30:30.130
- Oh!
- [laughs]

30:30.214 --> 30:31.839
Hi.
[laughs]

30:31.923 --> 30:34.839
[rhythmic remix of Beethoven's
"Moonlight Sonata"]

30:34.923 --> 30:41.964
♪ ♪

31:45.130 --> 31:47.089
[bright tone]

31:48.798 --> 31:49.631
We're gonna be late!

31:49.714 --> 31:50.714
Can I please just stay home?

31:50.798 --> 31:52.798
Everybody's going to church,
goddammit.

31:52.881 --> 31:54.673
♪ I'm gonna tell everybody ♪

31:54.756 --> 31:56.714
AMBER GEMSTONE:
Our son is back in our lives,

31:56.798 --> 31:58.381
and you need to give him
another chance

31:58.464 --> 31:59.297
because I love him.

31:59.714 --> 32:01.631
You got me opening a church
in the middle of a mall.

32:01.714 --> 32:03.631
This is a place
you can buy slacks,

32:03.714 --> 32:05.506
but now you can buy Jesus.

32:05.839 --> 32:07.881
But you can't put him
on layaway.

32:07.964 --> 32:08.923
(CHUCKLES)

32:09.255 --> 32:11.673
I brought you all here
because I have made a discovery.

32:11.756 --> 32:13.130
-Grab his ass.
-(SCREAMS)

32:14.506 --> 32:16.005
-SON: Hey, Dad?
-What's up-- huh?

32:16.089 --> 32:17.005
-What's going on?
-Help!

32:17.339 --> 32:19.005
Well I just wanted to talk,
but did he say, "Help"?

32:19.089 --> 32:20.422
Just go outside,
I'll be out there in a sec,

32:20.506 --> 32:21.756
I'm just gonna finish up
a prayer

32:21.839 --> 32:22.881
-with these guys.
-Okay.

32:23.172 --> 32:25.047
♪ (MUSIC CONCLUDES) ♪
